{"tid":466063,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"一個女仔去日本","createTime":"2017-11-12T07:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T02:00:33.000Z","uid":3599,"like":1,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"7a33cde7cfc41d62e554c0f3fe710a13d40ba7c0","tid":466063,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2882ea2401889f0ddca7b9ba8e4ae2893775d2","tid":466063,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:57:13.000Z","msg":"梅田 買到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4abf8d5e2abe0d8365e5511e868be8412282186","tid":466063,"uid":1587,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbeed8c173eeb0bc9a3ace002754be23f603c1a9","tid":466063,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d8218aba4067b822d711c598322e640884a807","tid":466063,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 8 月第一次自己去旅行 去咗11日，關西玩到關東<br />\n去得大阪去會唔會去京都？<br />\n大阪市內無咩野玩，如果係鐘意歷史/鍾意行博物館可以去大阪今昔館<br />\n不過場內說明都係日文，唔識日文就可以睇下啲展品就算<br />\n去得大阪梗係去海遊館撚下魚 不過真係好多支那人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都係果句，大阪市內真係冇咩特別嘢玩<br />\n建議擺多啲時間去京都<br />\n如果鍾意撚魚，推介你去京都水族館<br />\n雖然要去京都水族館要係京都駅行大約4個字<br />\n但入面氣氛好好，幾乎見唔到支那人<br />\n好多一家大細日本人仲有日本couple 會去<br />\n（去咗海遊館同京都水族館，感覺上京都水族館氣氛好過海遊館）<br />\n最大問題係海遊館太多人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除咗水族館之外，錦市場都係一個唔錯嘅選擇<br />\n要留意嘅係錦市場晏晝之後就開始閂門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n京都真係好多嘢玩，除咗一定要去嘅伏見稻荷大社<br />\n二条三条四条真係行到你唔行都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n特別要推介京都駅上面有條拉麵小路，成層都係拉麵舖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰度可以食到日本各種拉麵派系嘅拉麵，價錢都好實惠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">有J絲打</span>"},{"pid":"48e744ce149691e0096c2a24478eedc97a9e6009","tid":466063,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:40:05.000Z","msg":"p.s. 大阪今昔館有和服借嚟著，都幾受歡迎，但自己一個就... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc64bbdc624661a937959e544c8cd524edc4c0a","tid":466063,"uid":1587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:40:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eccc3487eff5dbc0745fe68dc9501fbdf5a6b41f","tid":466063,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:44:19.000Z","msg":"申手申到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939d80f7ea3960a28ab5209726c18cfda69e1d31","tid":466063,"uid":65142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a44084c0f17be34a0f88d0569f051c48baf191","tid":466063,"uid":65142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 8 月第一次自己去旅行 去咗11日，關西玩到關東<br />\n去得大阪去會唔會去京都？<br />\n大阪市內無咩野玩，如果係鐘意歷史/鍾意行博物館可以去大阪今昔館<br />\n不過場內說明都係日文，唔識日文就可以睇下啲展品就算<br />\n去得大阪梗係去海遊館撚下魚 不過真係好多支那人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都係果句，大阪市內真係冇咩特別嘢玩<br />\n建議擺多啲時間去京都<br />\n如果鍾意撚魚，推介你去京都水族館<br />\n雖然要去京都水族館要係京都駅行大約4個字<br />\n但入面氣氛好好，幾乎見唔到支那人<br />\n好多一家大細日本人仲有日本couple 會去<br />\n（去咗海遊館同京都水族館，感覺上京都水族館氣氛好過海遊館）<br />\n最大問題係海遊館太多人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除咗水族館之外，錦市場都係一個唔錯嘅選擇<br />\n要留意嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\">錦市場晏晝之後就開始閂門</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n京都真係好多嘢玩，除咗一定要去嘅伏見稻荷大社<br />\n二条三条四条真係行到你唔行都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n特別要推介京都駅上面有條拉麵小路，成層都係拉麵舖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰度可以食到日本各種拉麵派系嘅拉麵，價錢都好實惠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">有J絲打</span></blockquote><br />\n想問下係晏到幾點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一兩點?"},{"pid":"8451ba2fccc14932d6fc54c721aa66af4b129ba4","tid":466063,"uid":93395,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:08:46.000Z","msg":"同我食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9951390d2014b622c006e642b0be6225ad682d6d","tid":466063,"uid":10342,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見到咩岩就買黎食<br />\n講簡單英文佢地明，有些店有中文餐牌及懂國語店員。<br />\n<br />\n我記得搭升降機時有個婆婆用英文問我邊到黎<br />\n係唔係學生 吹左一陣水幾nice。去餐廳食完野落雨又送左把新雨傘比我用。係機場同朋友自動販賣機買野時我搵緊碎銀，有個鬼佬手持銀仔問我you want this?<br />\n當然到到都有壞人同好人，自己留意返。<br />\n<br />\n日本人英文都唔錯，唔會話講英文講到似日文咁。<br />\n唔好比某影片呃左。"},{"pid":"ca29f4bde7dabcf1332324af24ef732e6fee5651","tid":466063,"uid":51747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:39:27.000Z","msg":"連登仔去大阪都去信長書店，好似係。"},{"pid":"cd541ea44d4899a1890b7831981849a6386e2582","tid":466063,"uid":8122,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:40:54.000Z","msg":"飛田新地必去"},{"pid":"c82034b5d05941dbd4f4737190a2bc8b00e99b65","tid":466063,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1227ec0af12d2cbdde9ec32f9bf538599a09a5b5","tid":466063,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你走我就去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786df84ae4506f0623c170fbd25c5f2e59799e1e","tid":466063,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>p.s. 大阪今昔館有和服借嚟著，都幾受歡迎，但自己一個就... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己一個就唔着和服啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b8243970d73ae425fdd81a83f634618f9082b2","tid":466063,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"又要自己一個去又要圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我2月先去呀，利申絲</span>"},{"pid":"64ce69409163424663611b3bc9e9d0f301f67385","tid":466063,"uid":33424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飛田新地必去</blockquote><br />\n飛田唔會見到港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910036a5d3cc80c6d9c7061b6772dc80af6f0e99","tid":466063,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:58:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飛田新地必去</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36667fa3648340cbb52909c16bc925d304b228f4","tid":466063,"uid":46388,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:58:48.000Z","msg":"直上神戶仲好玩，遊客都少d，午餐食神戶牛平靚正，要買野去垂水outlet仲平仲好行過梅田，而且一月冬季大減價簡六日入去分分鐘會仲多平野買，咁冷既天氣仲可以去有馬溫泉行下再比幾百yen泡一泡溫泉<br />\n<br />\n大阪中心地帶同京都都變晒重遊客地區，黑門市場都貴左好多<br />\n<br />\nPs:一個女仔夜晚唔好去酒吧既地方，d醉酒架仔好煩"},{"pid":"28a6d4e5158cd8470b8107a5320489c0b956e1b6","tid":466063,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:59:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又要自己一個去又要圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我2月先去呀，利申絲</span></blockquote><br />\n問吓有咩好去阿嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80880dd7e9d946aaeb47b97f42e5d89ba0255b5c","tid":466063,"uid":92462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:59:40.000Z","msg":"京都仲有個水族館架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個好似少d聽人講"},{"pid":"7a41e2c21020e8be9d63a43c5a144565de607ae9","tid":466063,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 8 月第一次自己去旅行 去咗11日，關西玩到關東<br />\n去得大阪去會唔會去京都？<br />\n大阪市內無咩野玩，如果係鐘意歷史/鍾意行博物館可以去大阪今昔館<br />\n不過場內說明都係日文，唔識日文就可以睇下啲展品就算<br />\n去得大阪梗係去海遊館撚下魚 不過真係好多支那人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都係果句，大阪市內真係冇咩特別嘢玩<br />\n建議擺多啲時間去京都<br />\n如果鍾意撚魚，推介你去京都水族館<br />\n雖然要去京都水族館要係京都駅行大約4個字<br />\n但入面氣氛好好，幾乎見唔到支那人<br />\n好多一家大細日本人仲有日本couple 會去<br />\n（去咗海遊館同京都水族館，感覺上京都水族館氣氛好過海遊館）<br />\n最大問題係海遊館太多人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除咗水族館之外，錦市場都係一個唔錯嘅選擇<br />\n要留意嘅係錦市場晏晝之後就開始閂門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n京都真係好多嘢玩，除咗一定要去嘅伏見稻荷大社<br />\n二条三条四条真係行到你唔行都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n特別要推介京都駅上面有條拉麵小路，成層都係拉麵舖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰度可以食到日本各種拉麵派系嘅拉麵，價錢都好實惠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">有J絲打</span></blockquote><br />\n如果去京都嘅話係咪應該喺大阪玩一日跟住再去京都 之後再去奈良？"},{"pid":"2cdf10c007646a06fdac7df885dcb2547f3f7f0a","tid":466063,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直上神戶仲好玩，遊客都少d，午餐食神戶牛平靚正，要買野去垂水outlet仲平仲好行過梅田，而且一月冬季大減價簡六日入去分分鐘會仲多平野買，咁冷既天氣仲可以去有馬溫泉行下再比幾百yen泡一泡溫泉<br />\n<br />\n大阪中心地帶同京都都變晒重遊客地區，黑門市場都貴左好多<br />\n<br />\nPs:一個女仔夜晚唔好去酒吧既地方，d醉酒架仔好煩</blockquote><br />\n但得一個女仔有冇得浸溫泉架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我有紋身"},{"pid":"a222103e9b3be24f5a97683c951579e8cd9bde37","tid":466063,"uid":54371,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:01:02.000Z","msg":"女仔申手果然特別易<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b617291443e98295ada1ab0f6b7bf97a8837197c","tid":466063,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又要自己一個去又要圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我2月先去呀，利申絲</span></blockquote><br />\n問吓有咩好去阿嘛<img 