mal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">有J絲打</span></blockquote><br />\n如果去京都嘅話係咪應該喺大阪玩一日跟住再去京都 之後再去奈良？</blockquote><br />\n睇你住宿點安排，其實三個地方都係大約半個鐘至九個字車程<br />\n但日日都搭JR 車費會好重皮，又哂時間<br />\n我覺得就可以京都住，玩京都同奈良，大阪住，玩返大阪<br />\n唔好擺咁多時間係大阪市內 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家諗緊好唔好頭兩日就喺心齋橋嗰邊住<br />\n剩返果三日就喺京都住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以啊"},{"pid":"3c987b371d075c214b0d4f41893634e1f01e933d","tid":466063,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好想去多次京都水族館<br />\n啲企鵝好正，可以隔住塊玻璃望到佢哋<br />\n上次咁啱撞正佢哋餵企鵝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日都有海豚睇 （好似係） <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> real good</blockquote><br />\n海豚個環節有互動要用哨吹出聲<br />\n<br />\n聽唔明互動唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe925ee9c3811c409f6c46d86bf581ea246e3ac","tid":466063,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好想去多次京都水族館<br />\n啲企鵝好正，可以隔住塊玻璃望到佢哋<br />\n上次咁啱撞正佢哋餵企鵝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset