b6c3abd65f62383e39","tid":466063,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好想去多次京都水族館<br />\n啲企鵝好正，可以隔住塊玻璃望到佢哋<br />\n上次咁啱撞正佢哋餵企鵝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日都有海豚睇 （好似係） <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> real good</blockquote><br />\n海豚個環節有互動要用哨吹出聲<br />\n<br />\n聽唔明互動唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> boo boo boo boo</blockquote><br />\n長崎企鵝水族館仲正可以同佢地接觸玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似幾正<br />\n但係應該唔夠時間去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0187bfb29917a0c59f6744d983f15067a9050b58","tid":466063,"uid":6595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:23:25.000Z","msg":"留名1月獨遊，但機票都未買"},{"pid":"355e7853a1dddedfdf1f49fa8c11cef1716ac275","tid":466063,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大阪有條雪糕街好出名 不過好少遊客知</blockquote><br />\n上網好似搵唔到乜嘢係雪糕街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似唔知咩田新地幾有特色"},{"pid":"98d1faa2c044e9b8f01f16c1dcd82cb153942f7d","tid":466063,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大阪有條雪糕街好出名 不過好少遊客知</blockquote><br />\n上網好似搵唔到乜嘢係雪糕街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似唔知咩田新地幾有特色</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702bb948a3bd590057b58236206648ae80f0f270","tid":466063,"uid":3900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T07:11:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>直上神戶仲好玩，遊客都少d，午餐食神戶牛平靚正，要買野去垂水outlet仲平仲好行過梅田，而且一月冬季大減價簡六日入去分分鐘會仲多平野買，咁冷既天氣仲可以去有馬溫泉行下再比幾百yen泡一泡溫泉<br />\n<br />\n大阪中心地帶同京都都變晒重遊客地區，黑門市場都貴左好多<br />\n<br />\nPs:一個女仔夜晚唔好去酒吧既地方，d醉酒架仔好煩</blockquote><br />\n但得一個女仔有冇得浸溫泉架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我有紋身</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有紋身你就bye得啦"},{"pid":"3a2817232156cfd723b838898b2d866cb6372b1c","tid":466063,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T13:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a302066b154d6653f0d41cf2136b8316e780081a","tid":466063,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T13:51:57.000Z","msg":"我一月一個去東京<br />\n想浸溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128cb6c34cb238cbbde3b11128db5b1d0a9e790c","tid":466063,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T13:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d08f423b831f698b29b5e407eb2fc745f7009fd","tid":466063,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"如果一個人去環球影城一月使唔使買express"},{"pid":"66bcb9c2f06157ef395dad9360bfe30de8b02375","tid":466063,"uid":114750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T15:08:24.000Z","msg":"樓主現實係咪冇乜朋友"},{"pid":"b1fcd19f67321007e6c3e159d06c3d964a1795f7","tid":466063,"uid":30469,"like":0,"dislike":1